{"tid":2284532,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jimin歡呼「又長高了」擺脫最嬌小！驕傲點名兩成員：請準備一下囉","createTime":"2020-11-13T11:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f128371990a0010253e66920a5e49056842e5d","tid":2284532,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"南韓天團BTS防彈少年團成員Jimin最新公開自己的身高、體重，竟然發現自己又長高了！他不但PO網歡呼慶祝，還直接點名2位成員，「我追上了，下一位請準備」，不過他已經年滿25歲，但對自己身高胸有成竹的模樣，讓粉絲都笑爆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5268/d5268118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5268%2Fd5268118.jpg&h=754f54aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jimin驕傲點名兩成員SUGA與J-Hope。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\nJimin稍早在防彈官方推特PO出自己的「私密數字」，在去年3月6日測量時，他身高為173.6，但今年10月23日測量時已經長到174，足足多了0.4cm！而體重以前為59.1kg，現在則降為58.6kg，瘦了足足半公斤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5268/d5268116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5268%2Fd5268116.jpg&h=60c54698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jimin歡呼「自己又長高了」擺脫最嬌小。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\n他在推特先寫下「我的身高...（笑哭臉），哇嗚！！」感到相當興奮，然而他接著再度發文嗆聲團員，「我首先先追上玧其哥（SUGA本名）囉！下一位J-hope請（有心理上的）準備一下喔！」一副勢如破竹的發言，引起破萬粉絲上網朝聖！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5268/d5268117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5268%2Fd5268117.jpg&h=ac6f4606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jimin點名兩成員：請準備一下囉。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\n事實上Jimin是防彈7人中最嬌小，殿後於身高174的SUGA，現在等同宣布兩人「都是一樣高」，而他也信誓旦旦擺脫最矮地位，誓言追上官方身高公布為177的J-hope。"},{"pid":"8e6368a7eb55412ce4ade6e9b931efe4bc8a4ce0","tid":2284532,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4771672d20096f416bb4097c8fe679a5422b3c6","tid":2284532,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6368a7eb55412ce4ade6e9b931efe4bc8a4ce0","tid":2284532,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"on兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abd5085d5b4509bcaad813603295db4ba23b53c","tid":2284532,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4771672d20096f416bb4097c8fe679a5422b3c6","tid":2284532,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6368a7eb55412ce4ade6e9b931efe4bc8a4ce0","tid":2284532,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"on兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"好似吞食天地咁on鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}